                     <interp inst="t18250407-185-person980" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took up the prisoner on the 28th of March, at her house in the Colonnade. I found three duplicates on her, which answer to the things produced.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I throw myself on the mercy of the Court.</p>
